1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:49,280
[Story of Yanxi Palace]
[Episode 5]

3
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:53,800
Delicious.

4
00:01:59,979 --> 00:02:04,400
Eat all these here before leaving.

5
00:02:08,820 --> 00:02:10,740
Your Highness, you are too kind!

6
00:02:10,970 --> 00:02:13,510
You don't even mind that
I've eaten so much.

7
00:02:13,910 --> 00:02:16,120
Thank you, Your Highness.

8
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:19,940
Looks like she's really a stupid one.

9
00:02:22,079 --> 00:02:25,250
Quickly make her leave. She's annoying me.

10
00:02:25,610 --> 00:02:28,940
That's enough, stop eating.
Her Highness wants you to leave.

11
00:02:28,940 --> 00:02:30,800
I still haven't finished eating!

12
00:02:31,010 --> 00:02:32,710
Take it and leave with it!

13
00:02:32,930 --> 00:02:35,540
Ask the Imperial Household Department...

14
00:02:37,579 --> 00:02:40,710
what kind of people are they hiring now?

15
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:44,140
Isn't that person mentally-impaired?

16
00:02:44,890 --> 00:02:49,040
Your Highness, I don't think so.

17
00:02:52,060 --> 00:02:56,460
Do you mean she's pretending to be dumb?

18
00:02:56,970 --> 00:03:02,660
We'll know by sending
someone to monitor her.

19
00:03:13,450 --> 00:03:15,480
Silly.

20
00:03:19,780 --> 00:03:22,850
Are you at ease now?

21
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:27,260
Being careful will allow you to
sail a boat for thousands of years.

22
00:03:30,220 --> 00:03:32,200
I'm tired too.

23
00:03:32,579 --> 00:03:34,160
You can withdraw.

24
00:03:34,390 --> 00:03:35,950
Yes.

25
00:03:36,880 --> 00:03:40,350
Your Highness, rest well. I shall leave.

26
00:03:44,060 --> 00:03:46,220
What's wrong, Your Highness?

27
00:03:46,570 --> 00:03:50,140
I don't know why,
but I keep feeling something is off.

28
00:03:50,410 --> 00:03:54,740
Your Highness, you're still suspecting
that Wei Ying Luo pretends to be dumb?

29
00:03:56,470 --> 00:04:00,250
If she is pretending,
then she's someone to watch out for.

30
00:04:02,530 --> 00:04:04,660
Who doesn't know to pretend to be dumb?

31
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:08,130
Upon entering, she tripped.

32
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:10,600
She started talking in a silly manner.

33
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:14,130
This made Noble Consort assume
that she's mentally-impaired.

34
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:19,240
But the problem is, Noble Consort hadn't
even started to interrogate her yet.

35
00:04:21,529 --> 00:04:23,600
I don't understand.

36
00:04:25,660 --> 00:04:29,520
How long it takes for you to walk
from the Embroidery Workshop to here?

37
00:04:29,810 --> 00:04:32,020
She has guessed that Noble Consort
is planning to give her trouble.

38
00:04:32,020 --> 00:04:34,880
She then immediately
thought of a countermeasure.

39
00:04:36,340 --> 00:04:38,270
It's not hard to pretend to be dumb.

40
00:04:38,290 --> 00:04:41,350
What's hard is to dissipate
the anger of Noble Consort.

41
00:04:42,250 --> 00:04:46,390
Those seven bowls of lotus-root
powder balls just came in very handy.

42
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:14,610
It's so late.

43
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:17,380
Why is Ying Luo still not back?

44
00:05:18,390 --> 00:05:20,930
Did something bad happen to her?

45
00:05:22,390 --> 00:05:24,360
No, I must go check.

46
00:05:24,980 --> 00:05:26,430
Where are you going?

47
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:29,320
It's the Chuxiu Palace.
You don't want to live?

48
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:32,500
Ying Luo helped me before,
how could I just leave her?

49
00:05:32,880 --> 00:05:36,220
Ji Xiang, you are really silly.

50
00:05:36,540 --> 00:05:39,270
Does she need to spend
such a long time in Chuxiu Palace?

51
00:05:39,270 --> 00:05:42,460
In my opinion, she might have gone dating.

52
00:05:42,770 --> 00:05:45,370
Jin Xiu, this is the Forbidden City.

53
00:05:45,650 --> 00:05:48,670
At night, the ones left are just
palace maids and eunuchs.

54
00:05:48,670 --> 00:05:50,170
Who will Ying Luo be romantically meeting?

55
00:05:50,170 --> 00:05:54,220
Other than the Emperor,
there are other men too.

56
00:05:54,510 --> 00:05:56,909
The four Imperial guards
at the Qianqing Gates.

57
00:05:56,909 --> 00:05:59,909
The Report Officer at the Yuehua Gates.

58
00:06:00,310 --> 00:06:02,770
The two Imperial physicians
in the Imperial Pharmacy.

59
00:06:02,770 --> 00:06:06,090
That's seven men.
There must be one who's meeting her.

60
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:07,630
Shut up!

61
00:06:07,870 --> 00:06:10,580
If you continue to spout rubbish,
I'll rip your mouth!

62
00:06:10,580 --> 00:06:11,980
Did I say anything wrong?

63
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,950
Last time she wouldn't let
us see the Imperial Guards,

64
00:06:13,950 --> 00:06:15,400
while she secretly went out
to have a date now.

65
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:17,100
She thinks we don't have eyes?

66
00:06:17,420 --> 00:06:19,150
She's still not back.

67
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:22,220
Good thing that Madam Fang is sleeping.

68
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:26,080
Or else, she would be dead!

69
00:06:26,980 --> 00:06:28,770
You're still talking!

70
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:31,320
-Are you crazy?
-Enough! Stop hitting!

71
00:06:31,900 --> 00:06:37,140
Ying Luo might be in
big trouble this time.

72
00:06:37,950 --> 00:06:41,530
Ling Long, what did you say?

73
00:06:42,330 --> 00:06:43,590
This afternoon,

74
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:46,300
I saw Sister Zhi Lan's face
and it was so scary.

75
00:06:46,710 --> 00:06:50,320
Ying Luo might have
got into big trouble...

76
00:06:51,790 --> 00:06:53,360
and can never return.

77
00:06:53,590 --> 00:06:55,409
What?

78
00:07:00,900 --> 00:07:02,270
Ying Luo's back. She's fine.

79
00:07:02,270 --> 00:07:03,910
Ying Luo.

80
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:09,560
Ying Luo.

81
00:07:09,850 --> 00:07:11,550
Let's sleep.

82
00:07:14,090 --> 00:07:17,360
Ji Xiang, see, I wasn't wrong.

83
00:07:17,630 --> 00:07:19,660
Someone is guilty.

84
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:22,160
She heard it, but isn't talking.

85
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:25,820
She indeed has a lover.

86
00:07:26,090 --> 00:07:28,890
-You're still at it!
-I didn't say anything wrong.

87
00:07:29,010 --> 00:07:30,500
Let's sleep.

88
00:07:53,010 --> 00:07:54,720
You go first.

89
00:08:14,430 --> 00:08:17,490
Ying Luo, you two are not leaving?

90
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:21,630
No rush, Ling Long and
I haven't finished eating.

91
00:08:24,370 --> 00:08:26,450
I'll get going then.

92
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:38,720
Ying Luo, I need to go to the
Embroidery Workshop now.

93
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:46,350
Ling Long, I kept thinking
on my way back last night.

94
00:08:47,450 --> 00:08:51,000
Who could have leaked this
secret to the Noble Consort?

95
00:08:53,820 --> 00:08:55,800
How would I know?

96
00:08:57,610 --> 00:08:59,250
If you really don't know,

97
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:02,480
you should have asked what secret is that.

98
00:09:05,950 --> 00:09:08,180
Even if you don't tell me, I know.

99
00:09:09,170 --> 00:09:11,470
That day, you were in Yonghe Palace.

100
00:09:11,870 --> 00:09:15,870
Yesterday, you and Ji Xiang even
went out to deliver the spring clothes.

101
00:09:16,350 --> 00:09:18,930
Other than you, who else could it be?

102
00:09:19,500 --> 00:09:20,780
Ying Luo...

103
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:23,620
-Ying Luo, listen to me.
-What?

104
00:09:24,280 --> 00:09:26,990
You want Noble Consort Gao to
kill me so you can vent your anger?

105
00:09:26,990 --> 00:09:29,650
Or you want to tell me
the jealousy in your heart?

106
00:09:30,910 --> 00:09:34,220
Ying Luo, I admit it.

107
00:09:34,780 --> 00:09:37,260
I didn't watch my mouth, but I...

108
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:41,380
Do you know why I didn't confront
you when I returned last night?

109
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:46,480
Because I was too full that it hurt.

110
00:09:46,970 --> 00:09:50,120
Last night, I ate many bowls
of lotus-root powder balls.

111
00:09:51,370 --> 00:09:55,550
Ying Luo, what do you want to do?

112
00:09:59,110 --> 00:10:00,710
Eat it.

113
00:10:01,940 --> 00:10:02,960
What is this?

114
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:06,490
The lotus-root powder balls
that I brought home last night.

115
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:10,110
Don't worry, these were not vomited up.

116
00:10:12,170 --> 00:10:16,170
Ying Luo, we are good sisters that
entered into the palace together.

117
00:10:16,390 --> 00:10:18,990
Yes! Good sisters!

118
00:10:19,270 --> 00:10:21,870
We should share all
fortunes and misfortunes.

119
00:10:22,160 --> 00:10:24,540
Hence, eat it.

120
00:10:25,740 --> 00:10:29,190
I'm not eating!

121
00:10:29,930 --> 00:10:32,600
Eat it!

122
00:10:33,070 --> 00:10:35,210
You like to tell on others
behind their backs.

123
00:10:35,210 --> 00:10:39,650
If I don't block your mouth,
you will do it again.

124
00:10:42,140 --> 00:10:45,140
Eat it!

125
00:10:45,870 --> 00:10:47,890
Someone, come here!

126
00:10:48,290 --> 00:10:49,370
Shout!

127
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:53,200
Make it louder and let everyone hear it.

128
00:10:53,730 --> 00:10:56,640
Madam Zhang hates talkative
people the most anyway.

129
00:10:56,640 --> 00:10:59,410
Be careful or she'll cut off your tongue!

130
00:11:05,620 --> 00:11:07,480
I don't know any grand principles.

131
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:11,360
I just know if people don't offend me,
I won't bother them either.

132
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:15,420
If you don't finish this bowl today,
don't even think of going out this door.

133
00:11:15,420 --> 00:11:18,360
Eat it!

134
00:11:19,560 --> 00:11:22,510
If you still don't eat them,
I'll inform Madam Zhang that...

135
00:11:22,510 --> 00:11:24,320
you've associated with Chuxiu Palace,

136
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:26,850
the workshop can't
accommodate you anymore.

137
00:11:37,970 --> 00:11:40,120
You mustn't vomit one out!

138
00:11:49,670 --> 00:11:52,790
Ling Long, just directly
tell me if you envy me.

139
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:55,720
We can openly compete through
embroidery to determine the victor.

140
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:57,960
Resorting to underhanded tactics
because you fear of losing...

141
00:11:57,960 --> 00:12:00,090
will only make others look down on you.

142
00:12:00,250 --> 00:12:03,380
Hope that this bowl of
lotus-root powder balls today...

143
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:06,950
can seal your mouth and
make you remember this lesson.

144
00:12:25,590 --> 00:12:27,500
-Ying Luo.
-Madam.

145
00:12:27,830 --> 00:12:30,050
How is your illness?

146
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:34,360
The sun has risen from the west.

147
00:12:34,710 --> 00:12:36,800
My back was almost broken because of you.

148
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:38,520
You still dare to come here?

149
00:12:38,710 --> 00:12:39,910
Madam,

150
00:12:40,040 --> 00:12:43,380
I've always felt guilty about this matter
and want to make up for it,

151
00:12:43,380 --> 00:12:45,340
but we're too busy in
the Embroidery Workshop.

152
00:12:45,340 --> 00:12:47,060
Today, I finally got some free time.

153
00:12:47,060 --> 00:12:48,570
No need.

154
00:12:49,070 --> 00:12:52,170
I'll just slowly make you pay for it.

155
00:12:53,070 --> 00:12:54,860
That is in the future.

156
00:12:55,160 --> 00:12:57,740
Just let me help now.

157
00:12:58,130 --> 00:13:01,290
-Sister Bing Qing, let me do it.
-No need, just leave it to me.

158
00:13:01,290 --> 00:13:02,890
Give it to me.

159
00:13:03,150 --> 00:13:04,580
Wei Ying Luo!

160
00:13:04,780 --> 00:13:07,980
Madam, sorry! I didn't mean to!

161
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:10,040
You evil servant, leave!

162
00:13:10,230 --> 00:13:12,310
How about I accompany
you to clean your clothes?

163
00:13:12,310 --> 00:13:15,180
No need! Just get out!

164
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:23,200
Sorry, I really didn't mean it.

165
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:30,340
[Other than sister's knot,
could there be other clues?]

166
00:13:38,570 --> 00:13:40,270
What are you doing?

167
00:13:43,900 --> 00:13:48,470
How dare you steal things in my room?

168
00:13:49,250 --> 00:13:51,340
You're finally caught red-handed now.

169
00:13:51,340 --> 00:13:54,010
Madam, what are you saying?

170
00:13:54,310 --> 00:13:56,370
Didn't your clothes get wet earlier?

171
00:13:56,380 --> 00:13:59,490
I was looking for new clothes to give you.

172
00:14:04,610 --> 00:14:07,370
-Look.
-Put down the clothes and get out!

173
00:14:07,570 --> 00:14:10,240
-How about I help you to put them on?
-Get out!

174
00:14:13,600 --> 00:14:16,520
[When sister left the palace,
she didn't have any items with her.]

175
00:14:16,520 --> 00:14:19,000
[All her things were gone.]

176
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:24,000
[If she took them,
where could she have placed them?]

177
00:14:24,850 --> 00:14:28,250
You don't know?
She came back so late last night.

178
00:14:28,810 --> 00:14:31,210
-Didn't she go to Chuxiu Palace?
-I don't know.

179
00:14:31,210 --> 00:14:34,560
You're silly, she went for a date.

180
00:14:34,920 --> 00:14:36,040
-Who?
-A date?

181
00:14:36,210 --> 00:14:39,540
Her lover is an Imperial Guard
here in the Forbidden Palace.

182
00:14:39,630 --> 00:14:41,610
Is that true?

183
00:14:41,910 --> 00:14:44,280
You mustn't make
groundless accusations like that.

184
00:14:44,280 --> 00:14:47,340
Who's making groundless accusations?
I saw it myself.

185
00:14:47,490 --> 00:14:50,580
If a maid gets involved in a scandal
and Chief Wu learns of it,

186
00:14:50,580 --> 00:14:52,180
she'll get flogged to death.

187
00:14:52,270 --> 00:14:54,760
My eyes are not only for display.

188
00:14:55,070 --> 00:14:56,080
Tell us about it.

189
00:14:56,320 --> 00:14:58,850
Madam Fang went there
to catch them last time.

190
00:14:58,940 --> 00:15:02,250
She was too cunning that
she's able to escape.

191
00:15:02,650 --> 00:15:04,130
Next time, if you...

192
00:15:04,370 --> 00:15:05,940
Ying Luo.

193
00:15:07,570 --> 00:15:09,350
Come over here.

194
00:15:14,510 --> 00:15:17,770
What's there to be afraid of?
We didn't say anything wrong.

195
00:15:17,910 --> 00:15:20,310
I guess she won't be
able to return anymore.

196
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:28,370
Ying Luo, everyone is saying that
you have an Imperial Guard as a lover.

197
00:15:28,630 --> 00:15:30,570
Is there such a thing?

198
00:15:31,890 --> 00:15:35,330
Madam, do you believe rumours like that?

199
00:15:35,930 --> 00:15:39,250
Of course I don't,
but rumours get spread as it's true.

200
00:15:39,580 --> 00:15:42,430
The damaging effects
of rumors is quite huge.

201
00:15:42,750 --> 00:15:44,190
It's better that you be careful.

202
00:15:44,190 --> 00:15:47,790
I'm only doing the right thing,
there's nothing to be afraid of.

203
00:15:50,150 --> 00:15:54,120
I just fear that the rumors will get worse
as they spread and get out of control.

204
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:56,640
If it reaches the ears of Chief Wu,

205
00:15:56,930 --> 00:15:59,250
I won't be able to help you then.

206
00:16:02,170 --> 00:16:05,100
These things I'm telling you
are backed by evidence.

207
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:07,410
Thank you for warning me.

208
00:16:16,240 --> 00:16:18,320
Ying Luo, let's quickly go.

209
00:16:19,040 --> 00:16:20,490
Let's go.

210
00:16:25,460 --> 00:16:27,650
Those are materials
for the pottery workshop.

211
00:16:27,650 --> 00:16:29,830
Stop looking, let's quickly go.

212
00:16:41,640 --> 00:16:45,100
I just couldn't embroider a sunset cloud.
This is so annoying.

213
00:16:45,490 --> 00:16:47,690
Although Ying Luo has a bad temper,

214
00:16:47,950 --> 00:16:50,510
her embroidery skills are indeed superb.

215
00:16:50,760 --> 00:16:53,800
Or else, Madam won't
favour her that much.

216
00:16:54,170 --> 00:16:57,200
It shows that she is truly capable.

217
00:16:58,370 --> 00:17:01,260
Are you saying that I'm not skilled?

218
00:17:01,790 --> 00:17:06,650
Jin Xiu, I'm praising Ying Luo.
What does that have to do with you?

219
00:17:07,450 --> 00:17:11,930
So what if she's skilled? She keeps
having affairs with Imperial Guard.

220
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:16,450
One day, she will fail.

221
00:17:17,200 --> 00:17:19,319
What's the use of just saying it?

222
00:17:19,619 --> 00:17:20,960
Where's your evidence?

223
00:17:21,180 --> 00:17:25,990
Don't worry, I surely will get some.

224
00:18:59,880 --> 00:19:01,570
You do not know?

225
00:19:03,010 --> 00:19:06,220
Madam Fang, stop making it hard on me.

226
00:19:06,870 --> 00:19:09,080
I really don't know.

227
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:13,830
Do you really not know,
or afraid of Ying Luo and dare not say?

228
00:19:18,530 --> 00:19:22,530
Madam, Ling Long doesn't know, but I know.

229
00:19:23,340 --> 00:19:24,680
You know?

230
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:28,170
Last night, I personally saw
Ying Luo left our dormitory...

231
00:19:28,170 --> 00:19:31,900
and only returned around dawn.
She must have gone to meet her lover.

232
00:19:32,340 --> 00:19:34,340
You didn't follow her to have a look?

233
00:19:35,170 --> 00:19:37,760
Madam, I wasn't able to catch up with her.

234
00:19:41,410 --> 00:19:45,400
Ling Long, last time when
she met that Imperial Guard,

235
00:19:45,850 --> 00:19:47,680
what did he look like?

236
00:19:48,080 --> 00:19:50,180
Do you still remember?

237
00:19:51,240 --> 00:19:53,390
No, I don't remember anymore.

238
00:19:53,680 --> 00:19:56,440
Don't worry, just this one time.

239
00:19:57,150 --> 00:20:00,380
From now on, I won't bother you anymore.

240
00:20:02,610 --> 00:20:04,070
I'm unable to describe it.

241
00:20:04,120 --> 00:20:06,940
But if you let me see him,
I surely can recognise him.

242
00:20:06,940 --> 00:20:09,870
That's easy, I'll let Yu Jie
take you to identify him.

243
00:20:09,970 --> 00:20:11,290
No, you must not.

244
00:20:11,510 --> 00:20:12,790
This...

245
00:20:13,040 --> 00:20:16,370
Without any evidences,
how could I just go and point him out?

246
00:20:16,540 --> 00:20:20,860
Ling Long, it's fine.
Just go and identify him.

247
00:20:21,320 --> 00:20:26,070
Once you do it, your task with me is done.

248
00:20:28,150 --> 00:20:31,290
Okay, treat it as me helping you.

249
00:20:31,850 --> 00:20:33,880
But I will only identify the person.

250
00:20:34,270 --> 00:20:39,490
As for other matters,
I dare not get involved anymore.

251
