504
00:36:07,310 --> 00:36:11,210
This time, I have nothing more to say.

505
00:36:13,640 --> 00:36:16,180
Chief Wu, I've long heard that...

506
00:36:16,400 --> 00:36:19,720
you're fair in rewarding and punishing
while following the rules strictly.

507
00:36:19,720 --> 00:36:22,530
If others follow
Madam Fang in the future,

508
00:36:22,840 --> 00:36:24,780
by framing other people,

509
00:36:25,060 --> 00:36:28,000
and then slapping own mouth
as if nothing happened,

510
00:36:28,290 --> 00:36:32,210
then there will be no discipline
at all in this huge Forbidden City.

511
00:36:34,640 --> 00:36:36,870
Have you two heard it clearly?

512
00:36:37,130 --> 00:36:39,450
This is the Forbidden City.

513
00:36:39,640 --> 00:36:41,780
If everyone follows you two,

514
00:36:42,060 --> 00:36:44,770
this palace will have turned upside down.

515
00:36:45,120 --> 00:36:46,750
Men!

516
00:36:48,320 --> 00:36:51,760
Palace maid Jin Xiu envied
a colleague and sowed discord.

517
00:36:52,070 --> 00:36:54,830
-She will be caned 20 times and demoted.
-No.

518
00:36:55,110 --> 00:36:56,520
No, Chief Wu!

519
00:36:56,750 --> 00:36:57,770
Take her away!

520
00:36:58,060 --> 00:37:01,620
No! Chief Wu!

521
00:37:02,440 --> 00:37:04,920
No! Chief Wu! I was wrong!

522
00:37:05,280 --> 00:37:07,430
As for palace maid Fang Ni Zi,

523
00:37:07,560 --> 00:37:10,920
she gave false evidence against others
and committed offenses with her speech.

524
00:37:10,920 --> 00:37:15,890
Cane her 40 times and
expel her from the palace!

525
00:37:19,030 --> 00:37:21,130
Chief Wu, no!

526
00:37:21,350 --> 00:37:23,290
Chief Wu!

527
00:37:24,390 --> 00:37:28,710
Chief Wu!

528
00:37:30,270 --> 00:37:34,840
What place is the palace?
You people dare to create rumours?

529
00:37:35,650 --> 00:37:38,510
Whoever dares to gossip
or create trouble again,

530
00:37:38,800 --> 00:37:40,700
your ending will be like them!

531
00:37:40,910 --> 00:37:41,910
Yes!

532
00:37:42,090 --> 00:37:43,830
Yes!

533
00:37:44,460 --> 00:37:48,140
I'm so busy. How dare you invite
me to handle such a mess?

534
00:37:48,480 --> 00:37:50,870
-Madam Zhang.
-Yes.

535
00:37:51,250 --> 00:37:55,360
Make sure you discipline
these palace maids of yours.

536
00:37:55,820 --> 00:37:57,360
Yes.

537
00:38:08,080 --> 00:38:12,970
Madam, Chief Wu gave a little leniency
and allowed you to pack your things.

538
00:38:13,430 --> 00:38:15,560
You have to leave the palace in an hour.

539
00:38:15,830 --> 00:38:18,210
It's all your doing.

540
00:38:19,350 --> 00:38:24,940
If not because of you, I would be able
to leave the palace after six months.

541
00:38:25,620 --> 00:38:30,060
Now that I got expelled,
I not only lose my compensation,

542
00:38:30,870 --> 00:38:33,000
even my family won't dare to accept me.

543
00:38:33,080 --> 00:38:37,220
How is this my fault?
It's all a misunderstanding.

544
00:38:41,270 --> 00:38:45,430
Just tell me the truth...

545
00:38:45,810 --> 00:38:48,330
behind your stomach?

546
00:38:50,250 --> 00:38:53,180
You two kept spreading rumors
about me in the palace.

547
00:38:53,230 --> 00:38:55,060
You caused me to have
no place to hide myself from shame.

548
00:38:55,060 --> 00:38:57,190
The best way to eliminate rumours...

549
00:38:57,430 --> 00:39:01,500
is to escalate the matter and
let people know the truth.

550
00:39:02,990 --> 00:39:05,860
But how could I get you all to believe me?

551
00:39:06,210 --> 00:39:08,330
First, I must rendezvous often.

552
00:39:08,650 --> 00:39:12,910
I would make sure that you don't catch me.
You'd get anxious after a few times.

553
00:39:13,040 --> 00:39:17,820
Second, how could I fool others
without a real bulging abdomen?

554
00:39:18,610 --> 00:39:23,170
Hence, I asked for some kaolin
clay from the pottery craftsman.

555
00:39:23,680 --> 00:39:27,600
If you take it in small amount,
it won't kill but can bloat your stomach.

556
00:39:27,600 --> 00:39:30,400
I only looked a bit similar,
but you took the bait.

557
00:39:30,750 --> 00:39:33,070
You just can't wait to eliminate me.

558
00:39:33,340 --> 00:39:34,880
You're evil!

559
00:39:35,410 --> 00:39:37,120
You are like your older sister.

560
00:39:37,120 --> 00:39:39,280
A naturally-born lowly wretch!

561
00:39:40,290 --> 00:39:42,340
You finally admitted that
you knew my sister!

562
00:39:42,340 --> 00:39:45,370
Say it! How did my sister die?

563
00:39:45,800 --> 00:39:48,940
-Why is her knot accessory with you?
-I...

564
00:39:49,190 --> 00:39:50,950
I don't know.

565
00:39:51,440 --> 00:39:53,560
You really won't say it?

566
00:39:54,680 --> 00:39:56,900
Chief Wu got fooled earlier.

567
00:39:57,320 --> 00:39:59,640
He actually planned to
let you leave with nothing.

568
00:39:59,640 --> 00:40:02,900
If I inform him now the usual crimes
you do against the palace maids,

569
00:40:02,900 --> 00:40:05,060
what would he do to you?

570
00:40:05,340 --> 00:40:06,430
Don't tell him.

571
00:40:06,610 --> 00:40:09,140
Do you still remember
that white ceramic pot?

572
00:40:09,270 --> 00:40:11,590
It is a layer of soil on top.

573
00:40:11,870 --> 00:40:15,120
What's hidden under that
is my sister's ashes.

574
00:40:15,720 --> 00:40:19,490
I brought her into the palace
to seek justice for her!

575
00:40:19,880 --> 00:40:23,040
Say it! Tell me how did my sister die?

576
00:40:23,350 --> 00:40:26,350
How did she die?
Did it have something to do with you?

577
00:40:26,650 --> 00:40:28,910
I really don't know.

578
00:40:30,740 --> 00:40:34,400
Please don't go!

579
00:40:35,880 --> 00:40:37,120
I only know...

580
00:40:37,240 --> 00:40:40,910
that your sister committed a mistake
and was expelled from the palace.

581
00:40:40,910 --> 00:40:45,890
She gave me that knotted
accessory as a remembrance.

582
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:51,140
You still dare to lie!

583
00:40:51,980 --> 00:40:54,300
That knotted accessory was...

584
00:40:54,660 --> 00:40:57,080
personally made by me for my sister.

585
00:40:57,400 --> 00:40:59,840
On the night before my
sister entered the palace,

586
00:40:59,840 --> 00:41:02,680
I didn't sleep all night
to make 12 of them.

587
00:41:03,210 --> 00:41:06,090
I gave her the most beautiful one.

588
00:41:06,640 --> 00:41:09,810
My sister never removed that item.

589
00:41:10,400 --> 00:41:12,160
Why would she give it to you?

590
00:41:12,480 --> 00:41:14,290
I am wrong.

591
00:41:14,600 --> 00:41:17,570
I only secretly stole some
of her items and money.

592
00:41:17,940 --> 00:41:19,790
There's nothing more.

593
00:41:20,060 --> 00:41:21,740
Is that the truth?

594
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:24,520
It's true, I can swear by heaven.

595
00:41:24,760 --> 00:41:27,440
Your sister's cloth bag is over there.

596
00:41:27,870 --> 00:41:30,600
I'll leave them all to you.
I won't get any of them.

597
00:41:30,660 --> 00:41:33,040
I beg you to let me go.

598
00:42:00,210 --> 00:42:04,820
-Only these?
-The other money got spent by me.

599
00:42:06,050 --> 00:42:08,350
When I heard your name,

600
00:42:08,800 --> 00:42:12,520
I already found it familiar.
After giving it much thought,

601
00:42:13,270 --> 00:42:16,530
Wei Ying Ning changed her name
upon coming into the palace.

602
00:42:16,880 --> 00:42:19,370
Everyone used to call her Man.

603
00:42:21,040 --> 00:42:23,060
Hence, I didn't recall it right away.

604
00:42:23,060 --> 00:42:27,180
If I said any lies,
I will be hit by lightning!

605
00:42:32,370 --> 00:42:37,030
Ying Luo, let me remind you.

606
00:42:37,920 --> 00:42:40,600
Stop investigating about
your sister's death.

607
00:42:41,370 --> 00:42:44,910
She committed a huge scandalous act.
No one would dare to mention it.

608
00:42:44,910 --> 00:42:48,960
Liar! My sister isn't that kind of person!

609
00:42:49,890 --> 00:42:54,150
If you don't believe me,
you can ask Madam Zhang.

